data.description: This beautiful home at a FANTASTIC price offers INSTANT EQUITY in the renowned Blackstone Country Club Golf community. A MUST SEE!!! Experience the luxurious ambiance of this Lennar home with 3-car garage, fully finished basement, large backyard and open floor plan. This meticulously maintained home starts with fresh curb appeal, highlighted by new front yard landscaping. As you enter the home be welcomed by vaulted ceilings, 20 ft+ wall of windows in the living room that include Hunter Douglas window treatments throughout the home, an office w/ elegant French doors & hardwood floors in the entry & kitchen. The heart of the home, a spacious gourmet kitchen w/ gas cook-top & double oven. The kitchen boasts granite countertops, roomy walk-in pantry & wood shelves, large island & gleaming stainless-steel appliances. The dining area has walk-out access to a huge stamped concrete patio & Pergola- a perfect place for gathering around the gas fire pit w/ extra gas line for a grill. Yards kept lush & green by sprinkler system. The upstairs features a primary bedroom that exudes tranquility with an attached five-piece en-suite bathroom & large walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms share a Jack & Jill bathroom w/double vanity sink. A spacious, finished basement showcases laminate flooring, a 4th bedroom w/ closet & egress window. Check out the private gym w/option to make this room a 5th bedroom. There is NO bathroom currently in the basement but has plumbing for an additional bathroom to be added. Enjoy time watching your favorite movie in the media room of this basement. Park your vehicles in an attached garage equipped with two Chamberlain SMART garage door systems that open w/Amazon delivery services. Live the country club lifestyle, access to a 37,000 sq ft clubhouse, newly renovated fitness center, resort-style pool, golf & more.
